content: A lot of Finnish cities and villages have Swedish names that differ more or less strongly from the Finnish ones, and sometimes are completely different, even in meaning.
translations: ita:Molte città e villaggi finlandesi hanno nomi svedesi che differiscono più o meno fortemente da quelli finlandesi, e talv
